<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要有客人的到來，<delay8 />
這裡就會熱鬧起來，真是太棒了！<delay frames="40" />
請放鬆地好好享受喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然不是什麼很高級的房間，<delay20 />
如果你不嫌棄的話，<delay8 />
請當成自己家好好放鬆吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />如果這裡無聊到讓你想睡的話，<delay8 />
我先在這道個歉喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不好意思，<delay20 />難得你來到這裡，
我卻顯得有些精神恍惚<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種感覺，<delay8 />就是所謂的
「半夢半醒」嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我正嘗試把這個房間
裝潢成能讓人放鬆的空間喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你在這太過放鬆，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />導致想打瞌睡的話，
也完全沒有關係喔！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛才讀了一本名為<delay20 />
『夢之國的<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />』的書！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />主要是在描寫夢境中的故事，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />內容非常有趣喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我作夢都沒想到
今天會有客人來訪，<delay20 />
很開心能在這見到你！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這裡有點亂，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還請你在這好好放鬆喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>